Class Invitation

public class Invitation

    • Invitation

      public Invitation​(User invitationSender, User invitationReceiver, java.lang.String type, java.lang.String message)
      This is parameterize constructor for this class to set invitation sender, invitation receiver, type of invitation, invitation id. Creates reservation booked player, reserved playground, playground owner, price for reservation, and time of reservation.
      Parameters:
      invitationSender - This is player who send the invitation to another player.
      invitationReceiver - This is player who was sent the invitation.
      type - This is type of invitation if it is play invitation or join team invitation.
      message - This is the message which wrote in the invitation.
